OL,7,FMore than half of people who have
OL,8,Facted on financial advice they came
OL,9,Facross on social media said they ended
OL,10,Fup losing money, according to a bank.
OL,12,FOf the 31% of people who said they had
OL,13,Facted on financial advice on social
OL,14,Fmedia platforms, 55% said they had
OL,15,Flost money, the research, commissioned
OL,16,Fby TSB, found.
