OL,7,FNine in 10 (90%) people surveyed had
OL,8,Fseen an investment opportunity on
OL,9,Fsocial media, and more than two-fifths
OL,10,F(43%) would consider investing as a
OL,11,Fresult.
OL,13,FThe survey also revealed that more
OL,14,Fthan two-fifths (43%) of people felt
OL,15,Fworse about their finances after
OL,16,Fseeing posts about wealth on social
OL,17,Fmedia.
