OL,7,FSixteen to 24-year-olds were the most
OL,8,Flikely to feel downbeat after seeing
OL,9,Fposts about wealth (67%), followed by
OL,10,F25 to 34-year-olds (61%), with only a
OL,11,Ffifth (22%) of over-55s saying they
OL,12,Ffelt worse about their finances.
OL,14,FMore than 1,800 people who use social
OL,15,Fmedia were surveyed by Censuswide in
OL,16,FJune, for TSB.
