OL,7,FSurina Somal, director of everyday
OL,8,Fbanking at TSB, said: "While there
OL,9,Fcould be useful sources of financial
OL,10,Fadvice on social media platforms;
OL,11,Fthere are also pitfalls through
OL,12,Fincorrect information and unregulated
OL,13,Finvestments that could derail your
OL,14,Ffinances."
OL,16,FShe said that people should do their
OL,17,Fresearch to check that content is
OL,18,Faccurate, before jumping in.
