OL,7,FLast month, a crackdown took place to
OL,8,Fprotect social media users from rogue
OL,9,Fpromotions by some financial
OL,10,Finfluencers, or "finfluencers".
OL,12,FThe week of action started on June 2
OL,13,Fand involved the Financial Conduct
OL,14,FAuthority (FCA) in the UK as well as
OL,15,Fregulators from other countries.
