OL,7,FMany financial influencers acting
OL,8,Flegitimately and are not breaking any
OL,9,Flaws ` but others may tout products or
OL,10,Fservices illegally and without
OL,11,Fauthorisation through online videos
OL,12,Fand posts, where they use the pretence
OL,13,Fof a lavish lifestyle, often falsely,
OL,14,Fto promote success, the FCA said in
OL,15,FJune.
