OL,7,FSteve Smart, joint executive director
OL,8,Fof enforcement and market oversight at
OL,9,Fthe FCA, said in June: "Our message to
OL,10,Ffinfluencers is loud and clear. They
OL,11,Fmust act responsibly and only promote
OL,12,Ffinancial products where they are
OL,13,Fauthorised to do so ` or face the
OL,14,Fconsequences."
OL,16,FJenny Ross, Which? Money editor, said:
OL,17,F"Having a large following on social
OL,18,Fmedia doesn't mean that someone can be
OL,19,Ftrusted to give financial advice. In
OL,20,Fthe worst cases, they may even be
OL,21,Fpromoting scams.
