OL,7,F"Take the time to carefully consider
OL,8,Fany financial decisions, and don't
OL,9,Fallow yourself to be pressured by what
OL,10,Fyou see online ` particularly when it
OL,11,Fcomes to investments. However you
OL,12,Finvest, there's always a risk that you
OL,13,Fcould lose money. Always keep in mind
OL,14,Fthat if an opportunity sounds too good
OL,15,Fto be true, it probably is."
